"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:31:11.000Z","msg":"阿V偷望了一下，看見有一名墨綠色上衣、身形龐大的男子「癱屍」地上，有男警為他「搓心口」，其間女警曾高呼借剪刀，亦喊那傷者的名字，「醒呀醒呀，唔好瞓呀。」對方沒有回應。女警遂餵他喝水，他喝了一口，便將水全部吐出，五至十分鐘後，便有三至四名消防員將他圍住抬走，不知所終。後來看了記者會和報道，並與一些被捕者傾談，才發覺看見這場面的不止她一個。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bcbeda2fa008f569277c95c6c499c1fb5ea33c6","tid":1561453,"uid":242724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"蘋果終於爆料"},{"pid":"42f78235b0e0c3f6f09a5d89c9b411a67d389b23","tid":1561453,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"墨綠色上衣個個係咪成頭血個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇佢朋友係度阿"},{"pid":"fd4b616d082704d518fcfa96cb93c30edbc17666","tid":1561453,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:33:56.000Z","msg":"近了！"},{"pid":"2ead1803347fc95bd213ba1dd5947e7829074dc6","tid":1561453,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:34:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba15896ea091c144f288e2b3fe71ea7fcd5d957d","tid":1561453,"uid":242724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:42:28.000Z","msg":"仆街，消防的左個男仔去邊，前線有冇良心，可唔可以出黎講2句"},{"pid":"014f7322d51b64ef7457ce0dbf1f4d033c3241dc","tid":1561453,"uid":56328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42f78235b0e0c3f6f09a5d89c9b411a67d389b23","tid":1561453,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"墨綠色上衣個個係咪成頭血個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇佢朋友係度阿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:44:05.000Z","msg":"應該唔係, 果個係軍綠色"},{"pid":"fed8b0fd83f807e81d218b57b065fc4b2487f03c","tid":1561453,"uid":117968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:44:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}